---
title: Chipotle-Glazed Kumara Burger & Slaw with Tex-Mex Wedges & Chipotle Aioli
description: Welcome to a new world of veggie burgers. Instead of a meat patty, you’ll cook up a tasty kumara patty glazed in chipotle sauce, then pile it with crunchy slaw on a brioche-style bun. With a smear of plant-based aioli and spiced wedges on the side, this is a burger for the record books!

